596
00:32:50,210 --> 00:32:51,480
If you don’t wanna be scolded,

597
00:32:52,970 --> 00:32:54,240
then don’t be against him.

598
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:55,720
Start a business and get married.

599
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,480
Do as he pleases. That’s it.

600
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:59,360
I have a bookstore and sell poems.

601
00:32:59,360 --> 00:33:00,290
What else should I do?

602
00:33:00,290 --> 00:33:01,450
Only two books were sold,

603
