609
00:33:13,450 --> 00:33:14,600
Go back for some tea

610
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:15,920
and think about how to sell books.

611
00:33:16,490 --> 00:33:17,360
Won’t you drink with me?

612
00:33:17,360 --> 00:33:18,240
